Notes:

To run the daemon... just ./avmp.py -f -v javaMPJ.yaml up

To run the jobs.. Need to have...

1. Copy of the mpj-v0_44 files..
2. .bashrc needs x/y/z in it.
  - e.g.
  export MPJ_HOME=~/mpj
  export PATH=$MPJ_HOME/bin:$PATH
  export CLASSPATH=$MPJ_HOME/lib/mpj.jar
  export PATH=/usr/lib/jvm/java-1.7.0-opendjk-amd64/jre/bin/:$PATH

3. To compile - `javac -cp /home/jon/mpj/lib/mpj.jar HelloWorld.java`
4. To run - `mpjrun.sh -np 2 -dev niodev HelloWorld`
